.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32208ec99a213605207f81e224977017cb470aac","tid":2217761,"uid":75256,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"501ac27e0a2b561b90dfe514b8a77665aac01448","tid":2217761,"uid":100542,"like":119,"dislike":1,"score":118,"quote":{"pid":"1565603fc7b415de942610149666ed2abebdebbf","tid":2217761,"uid":39526,"like":51,"dislike":3,"score":48,"quote":{"pid":"cd5e9b79bd23eb20db24d5bf2776865497223784","tid":2217761,"uid":193642,"like":218,"dislike":2,"score":216,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T16:23:05.000Z","msg":"仲以為係香港樓"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T16:23:36.000Z","msg":"香港人會咩反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T18:03:42.000Z","msg":"請參考屎之戀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T04:44:14.000Z","msg":"剛剛上網睇海之戀個單位，竟然有人接手，仲賺到少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個買家係咪唔知爆屎呢單野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200531/K6KWRTKYE77AZE52WHG7HVH7EE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200531%2FK6KWRTKYE77AZE52WHG7HVH7EE%2F&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8Qfwzg2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=79036eea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200531%2FK6KWRTKYE77AZE52WHG7HVH7EE%2F&h=e512b4e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200531/K6KWRTKYE77AZE52WHG7HVH7EE/</a><br />\n張先生於去年8月正式將單位放盤，叫價1,200萬元，由於單位購入未足3年，由業主包10%的SSD稅。其後反送中運動越演越烈，市況越見嚴峻，經過兩個月單位仍未能成功放售，業主曾將叫價調低至1,150萬元。經歷社會運動、疫情及港版國安法打擊，「爆屎渠」單位最終的成交價與最初的叫價低219萬元，但賬面仍賺72.6萬元。但張先生表示，若扣除36萬元釐印費、買賣兩次的律師費共2萬元及支付地產代理佣金約9萬元，七除八扣後只賺約24萬元，形容:「只賺兩粒黃豆」。"},{"pid":"f951725a6c21c79cc21e2c830ff2c3384c763644","tid":2217761,"uid":296677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d82f5db4e7ed52a67a911f7089f73091815297e","tid":2217761,"uid":235277,"like":32,"disli